name: Symphony
body:
### Symphony Data Acquisition System
Symphony is a data acquisition system focused on electrophysiology experiments. Symphony allows research scientists to write user-configurable acquisition routines in MATLAB. It also provides an easy-to-use interface to run routines as part of an overall experiment.
